  "description": "## Deep Component Audit — hx-ripple\n\n**Component directory:** `packages/hx-library/src/components/hx-ripple/`\n\n### wc-mcp Tools — USE THESE\n- `score_component`, `get_component`, `get_design_tokens`, `find_components_using_token`\n- **Report wc-mcp bugs to `/Volumes/Development/booked/wc-tools` board.**\n\n### Audit Scope\n1. **Design Tokens** — `--hx-` tokens. Ripple color, opacity, duration. Dark mode.\n2. **Accessibility** — WCAG 2.1 AA. Reduced-motion support (prefers-reduced-motion). Decorative only.\n3. **Functionality** — Click ripple effect. Touch support. Programmatic trigger. Unbounded mode. Integration with buttons/cards.\n4. **TypeScript** — Strict. No `any`.\n5. **CSS/Styling** — Shadow DOM. Animation performance (transform/opacity only). Containment. CSS Parts.\n6. **CEM Accuracy** — All API documented.\n7. **Tests** — 80%+ coverage. Click trigger. Touch. Animation. Reduced-motion.\n8. **Storybook** — On button. On card. Unbounded. Custom color.\n9. **Drupal Compatibility** — Utility component. Twig-friendly.\n10. **Portability** — CDN-ready. Performance-critical utility.\n\n### Deliverable\nDetailed audit report. Fix CRITICAL+HIGH. Document rest.",
